Real Madrid face Atletico Madrid in the Champions League quarter-final first leg on Tuesday night . 
  Carlo Ancelotti says he is not obsessed with Atletico and says Gareth Bale will start . 
  Atletico are unbeaten in six Madrid derbies this season . 
  Real beat Atletico 4-1 in last season's Champions League final . 
  Sergio Ramos scored an injury-time equaliser in the final . 
 